item.title:
Sean Patrick Thomas has joined the cast of the upcoming ‘CRUEL INTENTIONS’ series reboot from Prime Video.
He originally appeared in the 1999 film as Ronald Clifford.
He will play Professor Chadwick in the new series, a new character who teaches at an elite university.
